          "reviewTitle": "Really lovely full coverage for mature skin\u2665\ufe0f",
          "reviewText": "Bought this for my mother, whom had had trouble finding the right medium shade for her that wasn\u2019t orangey but more olive toned. She\u2019s very happy with the formulation, as it\u2019s high coverage within being cakey, which as an aging woman she adores because it doesn\u2019t settle into fine lines or appear muddy. Just smooth and flawless! She was thrilled when I told her there were two! Will definitely be repurchasing and highly recommend for mature skin. It lasts all day with a smudge of primer and little baking and some setting spray. Hope this is helpful!",
