        {
          "reviewTitle": "It\u2019s ok. Pumps don\u2019t work and bottles aren\u2019t full.",
          "reviewText": "Ok. I normally wear Revlon color stay. I matched my shade with this brand. I saw a promo for this foundation but said \u201cI wonder if I can find it cheaper on Amazon. I did. I know being in the beauty industry that I may or may not in fact get the item in it\u2019s true form but whatever. It was a third of the price. So I\u2019ll start with comparison to my usual revlon color it was a match. Coverage wise, for me this had less coverage than my Revlon brand. It\u2019s also a tad heavy and very tacky. I had to use a setting powder because I didn\u2019t want gnats sticking to my face all day. It\u2019s not horrible but you do need to work with it. Lastly, the pump doesn\u2019t work and to my surprise when I opened the bottle I can assume it didn\u2019t work because there was very little product in the bottle. I will guess you get two bottle for a low price because each one is less than half full. I will more than likely stick with Revlon as it comes out to the same price and the coverage is better.",
